Operator       Description                                     Example
               Converts a positive value to a negative         x = -y

Pre Increment  Increment the value by 1 and then               x = ++y
               use it in our statement

Pre Decrement  Decrement the value by 1 and then               x = --y
               use it in our statement

Post           Use current value in the statement and then     x = y++
Increment      increment it by 1

Post           Use current value in the statement and then     x = y--
Decrement      decrement it by 1
